<!-- STORY 02 -->
<section id="story" class="story-02">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-12 title">
        <h3>Our Story</h3>
        <h5>A little about the bride and groom.</h5>
      </div>
      <div class="people">
        <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-6 col-md-offset-2">
          <%= image_tag "matt2.jpg" %>

          <p>Many things that made me always love you. Gentleness and courtesy everything can make me fly into the sky. Until probably can not think of myself before can love you. </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-6">
          <%= image_tag "jess.jpg" %>

          <p>Simplicity you showed, it can always make me happy. Serenity, honesty, happiness makes me endlessly mention your name in my mind. Thank you for everything. </p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

